text: {"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4eba9"}, "question": "What is FixConnect?", "keywords": ["what", "fixconnect", "about", "app", "purpose"], "answer": "FixConnect is a mobile app that connects customers with certified engineers for technical services. Find trusted professionals for electrical, HVAC, security, plumbing, and power solutions.", "category": "general", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebaa"}, "question": "How do I register as a customer?", "keywords": ["register", "customer", "sign up", "create account", "registration"], "answer": "Tap Register \u2192 Choose 'Customer' \u2192 Enter username, email, password, location \u2192 Verify email code \u2192 Continue.", "category": "registration", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebab"}, "question": "How do I register as an engineer?", "keywords": ["register", "engineer", "professional", "sign up", "trade certification"], "answer": "Tap Register \u2192 Choose 'Engineers' \u2192 Enter details and upload trade certification \u2192 Verify email \u2192 Continue. You can also set availability and write a description.", "category": "registration", "user_type": "engineer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebac"}, "question": "How do I reset my password?", "keywords": ["forgot", "password", "reset", "change password", "login problem"], "answer": "On login screen, tap 'Forgot password?' \u2192 Enter email \u2192 Verify code \u2192 Create new password \u2192 Change Password.", "category": "authentication", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebad"}, "question": "How do I book a service?", "keywords": ["book", "booking", "request", "service", "quote", "hire"], "answer": "From home screen: Request a Services \u2192 Fill service details (name, location, date, description) \u2192 Send Request \u2192 Review offers \u2192 Accept offer \u2192 Pay via Stripe \u2192 Confirm booking.", "category": "booking", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebae"}, "question": "What services are available?", "keywords": ["services", "categories", "electrical", "hvac", "plumbing", "security", "power"], "answer": "Available services: Electrical, HVAC Systems, Security Systems, Power Solutions, and Plumbing. You can request quotes for any technical issue.", "category": "services", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebaf"}, "question": "How do I request a quote?", "keywords": ["quote", "request", "price", "estimate", "cost"], "answer": "Tap 'Request a Services' \u2192 Enter service name, location, mobile number, service date, description \u2192 Upload image (optional) \u2192 Send Request.", "category": "booking", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb0"}, "question": "How do I respond to service requests?", "keywords": ["respond", "offer", "bid", "service request", "engineer", "accept"], "answer": "Check Services Request List \u2192 View Details \u2192 Select your price and time \u2192 Send Offer. You'll get notifications for new requests.", "category": "engineer_workflow", "user_type": "engineer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb1"}, "question": "How do I accept a job?", "keywords": ["accept", "job", "offer", "work", "take"], "answer": "From your Services Request List, tap 'Accept' on the job you want. Customer will be notified and you can start the service.", "category": "engineer_workflow", "user_type": "engineer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb2"}, "question": "How do I make payment?", "keywords": ["payment", "pay", "stripe", "billing", "money", "cost"], "answer": "After accepting an offer: Review payment details \u2192 Confirm Stripe payment method \u2192 Pay Now \u2192 Confirm Booking \u2192 Done.", "category": "payment", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb3"}, "question": "What payment methods are accepted?", "keywords": ["payment", "methods", "stripe", "card", "how to pay"], "answer": "FixConnect uses Stripe for secure payments. All major credit/debit cards are accepted through Stripe.", "category": "payment", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb4"}, "question": "Can I add extra payment?", "keywords": ["extra", "payment", "additional", "more", "tip"], "answer": "Yes, engineers can request 'Extra Payment' for additional work. You'll see this option during the payment process.", "category": "payment", "user_type": "both", "priority": 2}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb5"}, "question": "How do I cancel a booking?", "keywords": ["cancel", "cancellation", "remove", "delete", "stop"], "answer": "Go to Services \u2192 Find your booking \u2192 Tap Cancel. Check our refund policy for cancellation terms.", "category": "service_management", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb6"}, "question": "How do I reschedule a service?", "keywords": ["reschedule", "change", "time", "date", "move"], "answer": "Use the chat feature to contact your engineer directly to discuss rescheduling options.", "category": "service_management", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb7"}, "question": "What are the service statuses?", "keywords": ["status", "pending", "progress", "complete", "service"], "answer": "Service statuses: Pending (waiting for engineer), In Progress (being worked on), Complete (finished and paid).", "category": "service_management", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb8"}, "question": "How do I contact my engineer?", "keywords": ["contact", "message", "chat", "talk", "communicate"], "answer": "Use the built-in Messages feature to chat directly with your engineer. Available after booking confirmation.", "category": "communication", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebb9"}, "question": "How do I contact my customer?", "keywords": ["contact", "customer", "message", "chat", "communicate"], "answer": "Use the Messages feature to chat with customers. This helps clarify service details and coordinate visits.", "category": "communication", "user_type": "engineer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebba"}, "question": "How do I rate an engineer?", "keywords": ["rate", "rating", "review", "feedback", "stars"], "answer": "After service completion, go to Rating & Review screen \u2192 Rate service quality \u2192 Write review \u2192 Submit feedback.", "category": "reviews", "user_type": "customer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebbb"}, "question": "What are the subscription plans?", "keywords": ["subscription", "plans", "pro", "premium", "pricing", "cost"], "answer": "Plans: Free (\u00a30), Pro (\u00a320/month - 'Scaling Your Practice'), Premium (\u00a349/month - 'More Leads, Bigger Profits'). Engineers can upgrade for premium features.", "category": "subscription", "user_type": "engineer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebbc"}, "question": "How do I upgrade my plan?", "keywords": ["upgrade", "pro", "premium", "subscription", "pay"], "answer": "Go to Profile \u2192 Subscription \u2192 Choose Pro or Premium plan \u2192 Select Stripe payment \u2192 Confirm upgrade.", "category": "subscription", "user_type": "engineer", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebbd"}, "question": "How do I change my password?", "keywords": ["change", "password", "update", "security"], "answer": "Go to Profile \u2192 Security \u2192 Change Password \u2192 Enter current and new password \u2192 Save changes.", "category": "profile", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebbe"}, "question": "How do I log out?", "keywords": ["log out", "logout", "sign out", "exit"], "answer": "Go to Profile \u2192 Log Out \u2192 Confirm 'Yes, Logout' in the dialog box.", "category": "profile", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebbf"}, "question": "How do I update my profile?", "keywords": ["profile", "update", "edit", "information", "details"], "answer": "Go to Profile \u2192 User Information \u2192 Edit your details \u2192 Save changes. Engineers can also update trade certification here.", "category": "profile", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebc0"}, "question": "What is the refund policy?", "keywords": ["refund", "policy", "money back", "return"], "answer": "All purchases are final. No refunds once service is revealed due to digital/time-sensitive nature. Contact support for technical issues.", "category": "policies", "user_type": "both", "priority": 2}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebc1"}, "question": "What data do you collect?", "keywords": ["privacy", "data", "information", "collect", "personal"], "answer": "We collect: name, email, payment info, usage data, and communication preferences. We never sell your information to third parties.", "category": "policies", "user_type": "both", "priority": 2}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebc2"}, "question": "I'm not receiving notifications", "keywords": ["notifications", "alerts", "not receiving", "missing"], "answer": "Check your device notification settings for FixConnect. Ensure notifications are enabled in app settings and device settings.", "category": "troubleshooting", "user_type": "both", "priority": 2}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebc3"}, "question": "The app is not working properly", "keywords": ["app", "not working", "bug", "error", "problem", "issue"], "answer": "Try closing and reopening the app. If issues persist, update to the latest version or contact support through Profile \u2192 Legal and Policies.", "category": "troubleshooting", "user_type": "both", "priority": 2}

{"_id": {"$oid": "683564f9ce48e00826a4ebc4"}, "question": "How do I get support?", "keywords": ["support", "help", "contact", "assistance", "customer service"], "answer": "For support, go to Profile \u2192 Legal and Policies \u2192 Contact Support, or reach out through the in-app messaging system.", "category": "support", "user_type": "both", "priority": 1}
